# 著作权法

## 概述

William Landes/Richard Posner, An Economic Analysis of Copyright Law

知识产权固然是一套激励产权的制度,但是社会在缺失产权制度的情况下依然会一定程度上替代性地弥补产权制度的激励举措.

## 替代机理措施

1. The copy may be of inferior quality, and hence not a perfect substitute for the original.
2. Copying may itself involve some original expression - as when the copy is not a
literal copy but involves paraphrasing, deletions, marginal notes, and so on - and so a
positive cost of expression.
3. Copying takes time, so there will be an interval during which the original publisher
will not face competition.
4. There are contractual alternatives to copyright protection for limiting copying.  
合同法可以一定程度地替代著作权法.出版社对作者的合同有相当的利润承诺或稿酬,可以限制出版商印多少份.聚合平台出现(第三方链接),第三方对著作权的侵权是过去几年的热门官司.如果合同履行得好的话,合同能够一定程度上替代知识产权的保护.  
德国著作权法专家欧一根woma,作为伯尔尼公约?的主要修订者,在亚马逊德国购买了它的81年的书,似乎是用户众筹型的.他们曾经授权过亚马逊,但已经失效了.  
博士论文售出2800多本,但是不太相信,前面涨得快,后面长得慢.
5. Since a copier normally must have access to a copy in order to make copies, the
creator may be able to capture some of the value of copies made by others by charging a high price for the copies he makes and sells.
6. Many authors derive substantial benefits from publication that are over and beyond any royalties.  
比如说可以拿诺奖,评职称等.


